Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 2024-11-18
Welcome to SpaceMaster! At SpaceMaster, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal data is handled securely and transparently. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app and services.
Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:
Device Information:
Details about your device, such as model, operating system, and unique device identifiers, to optimize app functionality.
Usage Data:
Information about your interactions with the app, such as features used, session duration, and app performance.
Files Metadata (Optional):
If you use features like file compression or secret space, we may process metadata (e.g., file type and size) without accessing the actual content.
How We Use Your Information
The information we collect is used to:
Optimize app performance and provide core functionalities.
Improve user experience by analyzing app usage patterns.
Deliver premium features such as storage optimization and file compression.
Ensure data security for features like secret space.
Data Protection and Security
We prioritize the security of your data and use industry-standard measures to protect it. This includes encryption and secure storage for sensitive features like secret space. However, no system is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Third-Party Services
We may integrate third-party tools for analytics, advertising, or other services. These tools may collect and process data under their own privacy policies.
Examples of third-party services we may use include:
Analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics for app usage insights).
Advertising partners for relevant ads.
User Choices and Controls
Data Access:
You can view and manage the data stored within the app through the app settings.
Opt-Out:
You may disable analytics tracking or personalized ads in the app’s privacy settings.
Account Deletion:
If applicable, you can request to delete your account and associated data by contacting us.
Children’s Privacy
SpaceMaster is not designed for children under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware of such data, we will delete it promptly.
Updates to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our app or legal requirements. The latest version will always be available within the app or on our website.
